==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Harmless
<hw>Harm"less</hw> <pr>(h⟦aum⟧rm"l⟦ecr⟧s)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>Free from harm; unhurt; <as>as, to give bond to save
another <ex>harmless</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Free from power or disposition to harm; innocent;
inoffensive.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧ The <xex>harmless</xex> deer.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Drayton</au></rj></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Innocent; innoxious; innocuous; inoffensive;
unoffending; unhurt; uninjured; unharmed.</syn></p>

<p>--<wordforms><wf>Harm"less*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos>-
<wf>Harm"less*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms></p>

<p><ent>Harmonical</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>Harmonic</ent>⟦br⟧
<mhw>
